Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运气也是推理的关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.70,0:00:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的事情也能看的清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的故事发生在旅途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连句会上的罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.90,0:00:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.70,0:00:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却智慧过人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.80,0:00:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.79,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,Something' just not right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.96,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,在追寻着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.48,0:00:26.69,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯了谎言 现在也一样 fake your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.43,0:00:32.71,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,The start of century
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.21,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,一切毫无定数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.23,0:00:41.28,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,即使一个人也不能哭泣软弱 hate myself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.57,0:00:51.06,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,与真实的痛苦相反的是 埋藏在心中的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.55,0:00:59.87,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 映射出来 朝着两个人所决定的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.50,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.87,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,朝着没有尽头的黑暗前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.23,0:01:13.21,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有未知的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.50,0:01:18.22,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah.You're going nowhere .It's only destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.49,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,切实的前行着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.78,0:01:28.83,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,感受现在 You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.92,0:01:32.87,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.80,0:01:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋季的某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去岛根县松江旅游的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.60,0:01:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在松江温泉遇到连句会的5个会员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.00,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.00,0:01:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5人中的牛洼刚三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在松江城的游步道上被杀害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右手食指指着某个方位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是什么死亡留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人十有八九
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那四个人当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连句会决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.30,0:02:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,松江玉造连句十四次胜负(后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.20,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始连句会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一共有14句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是连句14
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.70,0:02:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让初学者毛利先生也能参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用文字接龙的规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是文字接龙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要遵守一点规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.40,0:02:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要从和树木有关的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二句就要很快地说出一个凶猛的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.70,0:02:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在请说出一个平常都能用到的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.20,0:03:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后从14句当中加入旬和佳节等数句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中间加入关于月亮的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的两三句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第13句是关于花的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.00,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的结尾句以春天愉快收场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做做试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先说发句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家说说自己作的句子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,众神也 聚来观赏啊 鹿之窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木泽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大龟旁 螳螂把斧子 高高扬起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.90,0:03:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摇曳的枫树 朝向日光的方向 红叶飞舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有牛洼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋高气爽 我的人生里 没有忧愁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作的都很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次为了祭奠牛洼的亡灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用他的那句作发句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么谁来作肋句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是肋句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是第二句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.40,0:04:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和发句有同样的韵 还要有标点符号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寂静之中 木实落下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着是八木泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸能作出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像没戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月光明亮 然后就来了吸血鬼 凑上一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.10,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼这个凶猛的人物很有新意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个也行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三句脱口而出就很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始跟着自己的想像走就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着想像走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲义 是日本制造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.40,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按韵不如说课本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然简单了一点 不过没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在轮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接上一个字尾是h的句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把犯人 抓给你们看 就是名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很新奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.80,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名侦探的世界和吸血鬼的世界很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点跳句的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过挺好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面该我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此行的目的是 发现神的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是礼子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名侦探的积极态度被一挥而散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么简单的可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,类人猿 脸长得很像 邻居的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第7字“我”是重点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在大厅捡到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是傻瓜 又丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.40,0:06:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家很厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.80,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.80,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下3句了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还找不出来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最开始你作的关于红叶的连句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说是坐在武家故居的休息场上根据看见的景色而作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我去了武家故居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在休息场是看不见红叶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是在其它的地方看见的红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其它地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么是在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉是犯人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要撒谎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没准就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉是为了那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样也解释不了牛洼死时留下的信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个人为什么要这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生让我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.20,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说让背着安来警探帮忙查查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没弄错的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人很可能就是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.30,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛洼死的时候要告诉我们的信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的手指不是指着竹子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是指着竹子前面的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.90,0:09:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿过游步道直指崛川对面的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.30,0:09:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是美杉去看红叶的武家故居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.20,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个第10句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是爱情的句子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是单相思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木泽昨天晚饭的时候点过眼药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.50,0:09:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉单相思的是八木泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以美杉昨晚就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛洼对八木泽说话很不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.10,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉看见了很为八木泽担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉 你是不是在掩护八木泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.40,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉昨晚听见牛洼和八木泽的谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是就改变了计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去松江城见了牛洼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.90,0:10:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里美杉看见的确是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没看见那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.00,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实话实说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是 老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.50,0:11:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随口就说出来了 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.80,0:11:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的喜欢什么人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的为他着想的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来要去的不是松江城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是月照寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很为八木泽担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.20,0:11:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是中途碰巧看见去松江城的公共汽车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见八木泽也在车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻跟着去了松江城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是等我到达游步道的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛洼已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个手指指向的方向…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我急忙回到武家故居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在休息场平静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到了该回来的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就回到了旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我确实去了松江城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我没杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没去游步道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你去了松江城的哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稻荷神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个有很多狐狸像的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他叫我去那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.60,0:12:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是牛洼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.50,0:12:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到达月照寺后30分钟左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛洼突然给我发了短信来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.30,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在立刻到松江城的稻荷神社来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.90,0:12:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我10点5分左右到达神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在那里等了大约15分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛洼没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给他打电话也没有回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我就回到月照寺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作了大龟的那句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你的眼药水会掉在现场呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.00,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我说的都是真的 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.20,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是觉得我说谎了 请去看看牛洼的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.90,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手机的履历已经都查过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.40,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有给你发过短信的履历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.60,0:13:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预备的手机查了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.60,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛洼说在包里还预备了一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的东西都检查过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手机只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.40,0:13:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你偷了牛洼的预备手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.60,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后给自己发的短信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.80,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安来警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凶器找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扔在月照寺的喷水池里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特制警棍用雨衣包着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.80,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面沾着的血液和被害人的血型一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个雨衣上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是铁证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我回警察局问话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.20,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都觉得是个误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一句让我说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开头字母是Q吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力糖果 快给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是连句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是从蚂蚁的道联想到的巧克力糖果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子式的可爱的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一句是花的句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎名 你说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.20,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 开头字母是I
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说个好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.40,0:15:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 女儿和我两个人 花的寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.30,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这句和刚才毛利叔叔给我念的那句一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.70,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.00,0:15:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸什么时候作的这么一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.80,0:16:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.10,0:16:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这句确实不是我作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.10,0:16:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天在大厅里遇到的浪花证券的友永作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.80,0:16:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后牛洼把它记在手册上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.40,0:16:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.70,0:16:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定以为是牛洼作的句子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为那样差劲的人怎能作出这么漂亮的句子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果就从手册上撕下了那一页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你把牛洼杀害之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.80,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在你自己的连句里面夹着暗语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第7句的第7字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第9句的第9字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第11句的第11字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我写下的挑衅的那句的报复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接在自己的句里面加上信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑警察和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷乐着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照你的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为只要有条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.20,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就一定会把从牛洼那里偷来的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.70,0:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说成是自己所作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这句是你非常喜欢的一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢富有感情色彩的句子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲思念女儿那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至于条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.10,0:17:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是八木泽作为犯人被带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及第13句花的句的第一个字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和前面那句的结尾发音一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.20,0:17:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说柯南刚才说的那句是爸爸让他说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我推理的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把从牛洼那里偷来的句子念出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是给自己庆祝胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.90,0:18:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连句的暗语只是恶作剧而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.20,0:18:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那句是昨晚牛洼给我看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 我有不在现场的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在现场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10点5分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.10,0:18:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在庭院美术馆的英国庭院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.00,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见一个迷路的孩子被交到他父母手里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才才想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事情装个摄像机就能办到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装在灌木丛的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.30,0:18:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南在客人散去后找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上你到了庭院美术馆之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在灌木丛下面安装了摄像机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.40,0:18:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用偷来的牛洼的备用手机给八木泽发了短信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后去松江城杀害了牛洼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:19:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又把八木泽的眼药水放在牛洼的手指前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.10,0:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在月照寺扔掉雨衣和凶器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去庭院美术馆拿回摄像机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.40,0:19:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就若无其事地回到旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣的推理 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有证据的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛洼死之前给我们留下的死亡留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那既不是指着竹子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是武家故居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是指数字「１」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.70,0:19:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连句的第一句是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.10,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椿警探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.10,0:19:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鉴定结果怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.30,0:19:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这双登山鞋左脚左侧最上面的钩子边上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了牛洼沾着血的右手手指的指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:19:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.90,0:20:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是想说你的鞋子的钩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我推测你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光注意到牛洼的手册里的句子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就没注意他摸了你的鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我输了 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.60,0:20:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实是我杀了牛洼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.30,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.20,0:20:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么觉得我奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最初让我感到奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是昨晚抽签的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常做签的人最后才抽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你却是第二个抽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.30,0:20:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面按照年龄来抽 该我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时你在签上作了手脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让牛洼抽到了容易作案的地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己则抽到最远最容易做不在现场证明的地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是日本第一的名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀害牛洼的动机果然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:21:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗了我们的钱 怎么能饶过他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 你也没有权利裁决他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.60,0:21:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.60,0:21:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够裁判他的只有神明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是神明为了让我明白这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.40,0:21:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才让你来到这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.30,0:21:41.08,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然等待着刺激的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.61,0:21:47.72,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,但最重要的还是眼前的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.98,0:22:00.27,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕会失去什么 但我们手中并没有掌握什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.77,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.90,0:22:07.61,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,在这蔚蓝的地球上 重复着无限的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.87,0:22:12.85,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,can make me free 就好想感受这样的悸动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.94,0:22:14.28,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.41,0:22:20.06,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉轻舞飞扬 在天空和大海之间烙上痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.31,0:22:29.86,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧地将你抱入怀中 想展翅高飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.00,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.16,0:22:38.88,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉轻舞飞扬 在天空和大海之间烙上痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.17,0:22:48.52,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧地将你抱入怀中 想展翅高飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.60,0:22:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.70,0:23:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美杉的心意八木泽好像明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.40,0:23:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 礼子老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.00,0:23:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连句还剩一句没完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.40,0:23:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了表达对毛利的感谢之情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.60,0:23:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有对松江的喜爱之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.20,0:23:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫卡狄欧汉 微笑的春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.40,0:23:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.10,0:23:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.30,0:23:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫卡什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.20,0:23:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫卡狄欧汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.00,0:23:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是小泉八云吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小泉八…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.50,0:23:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是"拉夫卡狄欧汉 困倦的春天"啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.10,0:23:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何小偷要偷这个破庙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.50,0:23:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要偷大笔善款的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.50,0:23:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边看上去也没有许多捐款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.50,0:24:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.70,0:24:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.20,0:24:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.60,0:24:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以证明小偷非去帝丹神社的理由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.90,0:24:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.20,0:24:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世间奇妙的天罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.90,0:24:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.40,0:24:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捐赠箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.60,0:24:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集是出人意表的迷案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 爸爸的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.30,0:24:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天谴啊
